overview: Big Tits Boss Volume Thirteen is another portion to the Reality Kings series "Big Tits Boss". Alison Star, Dawson Dalet, Heather Summers, Diana Prince, Kortney Kane and Tanya Tate are using their authority to get a piece of the action. Ramon Nomar is amongst the hung hunks and he gets to work out the details of his promotion. Enjoy the cross between business and pleasure.
tagline: Busty Bossy Bitches Gettin' Boned Big Time!
title: Big Tits Boss 13
